{"tid":920806,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"車子曬太陽就能不斷電跑250公里　德國SONO推太陽能車「Sion」","createTime":"2018-11-29T05:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T06:48:45.000Z","uid":212399,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"13d92e81a5b3208144aa90b556582d711999c734","tid":920806,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T05:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3726/d3726127.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3726%2Fd3726127.jpg&h=d15aade0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德國車廠SONO日前也正式公布旗下首款太陽能車款Sion的各項相關資訊。<br />\n隨著全球排污法規日趨嚴苛，近年來也有越來越多車廠著手投入替代能源車款的開發作業；除了行之有年的鋰離子電池、氫燃料電池甚至是已經投注量產的Hybrid油電、PHEV插電式油電車款外，更有品牌針對太陽能車款進行實測開發；日前德國獨立車廠SONO Motors便公布其太陽能車款Sion的各式相關資訊，該車款只需透過太陽能充電，即可繳出250公里的續航力表現。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3726/d3726128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3726%2Fd3726128.jpg&h=087abf4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3726/d3726131.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3726%2Fd3726131.jpg&h=004eb024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n透過車外共計330片的太陽能板，Sion即可繳出不遜於傳統電動車的續航力表現。<br />\n德國新創獨立車廠SONO Motors所打造的全新太陽能車款「Sion」，其電力來源主要是來自於鋪設於車門、車尾、引擎蓋等處共計330片的太陽能板；根據實測顯示，在陽光充足的天氣下，Sion每日可補充可供行駛30公里的車用電力，同時透過高能量密度的35kWh電池組，確保車輛能有最為充足的續航力表現。<br />\n除了250公里的續航里程數外，Sion在電力充足的條件下，其設置的電動馬達能繳出換算值163匹、28.3公斤米的最大峰值輸出；並能繳出9.0秒破百加速、極速140km／h的動態成績；雖說該數據與傳統燃油車款相比，似乎少了些惹人垂青的誘因，但要因應都會代步需求，已可算是從容以對。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3726/d3726129.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3726%2Fd3726129.jpg&h=c4d0bfd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3726/d3726130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3726%2Fd3726130.jpg&h=cce4b0ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSONO Motors表示，Sion目前已收到了近5,000張的訂單。<br />\n然則隨著全球環保意識興起，諸如SONO Sion這類替代能源車款也逐漸受到消費者關注；SONO Motors也表示，目前Sion也收付了近5,000張的訂單；但在正式投產之前，工程團隊仍在致力於降低電池組、動力結構的生產成本，藉此達到新車售價1.6萬歐元（新台幣55.7萬元）的既定目標，未來原廠也計畫採用電池月租制的配套方案，讓太陽能車能夠在全球市場得以普及化。<br />\n<a href=\"https://speed.ettoday.net/news/1317952\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspeed.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1317952&d=25Bn80kblrlf5eFaRga00qEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=06cb879d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://speed.ettoday.net/news/1317952</a>"},{"pid":"ce0d8612d75076096487c39fe0bce522d59a9b90","tid":920806,"uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T05:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1385f8a407906571b5291737d99478ef27f526f","tid":920806,"uid":198932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T06:14:56.000Z","msg":"之後要維護換太陽能板點計法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37f1f21a2c97616b9ef00e17b1239c8f18ac470","tid":920806,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T06:16:13.000Z","msg":"陽光充足的天氣下，Sion每日可補充可供行<strong>駛30公里</strong>的車用電力，"},{"pid":"783f7bab14a7bce5412633c433b8b2ddf37cb4f6","tid":920806,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T06:18:09.000Z","msg":"油組又要做野了"},{"pid":"4a340d7b5378cac78bb7677ea37d0790425da377","tid":920806,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T06:21:16.000Z","msg":"1.6萬<br />\n先十幾萬港紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7d79decd38b82aeb9e10d3410b58e1b8943ee5","tid":920806,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T06:27:13.000Z","msg":"要曬幾多日先行到一個鐘"},{"pid":"968f2e080dc5c9cfffb9dd995b8f2ce1016ac595","tid":920806,